description:
On today’s show, Emily is live from Greece with comedian and boyfriend Ben Morrison to talk about traveling with a partner – which also means vacation sex.

They give some insight to their first trip away as a couple, ways to amp up vacation sex – including what toys are best for travel and their favorite new position. Plus, how you can navigate some of those difficult couple conversations – because everybody has them – even the experts.
